{"tid":1485890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進］今日總結，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制，請大家對手足保持體諒嘅態度","createTime":"2019-08-18T17:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T07:10:58.000Z","uid":226955,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ef783a844cd2cfe0f590df329b6cb8438c478450","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:05:13.000Z","msg":"首先大家可以睇番喺金鐘手足全面散水之前我所講嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2412061705701511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflyingshadows%2Fvideos%2F2412061705701511&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cVgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=da762dbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2412061705701511</a><br />\n<br />\n斷正，黑警扮示威者收工返警總<br />\n<br />\n記得有巴打講過紅土遊行之後有班示威者行到旺角警署出面，有一個鬼不斷叫在場人士留低，又不斷話「點解要走呀？」之類嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但明明當日冇計劃過任何嘅圍堵行動，我相信宜家金鐘都係一樣情況，都係有班鬼不斷叫人唔好走，宜家共識都係叫走，到呢一刻喺現場仲叫留低嘅人好大機會係鬼<br />\n<br />\n我可能無能力勸到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我只係希望大家可以智勇雙全，理性啲講，宜家仲keep住要留低嘅仲有啲乜嘢目標？我剩係知道今日嘅戰略目標（搶佔國際輿論）已經超標完成，到呢一刻仲要留低對成個運動仲有乜嘢positive effect ？定係比黑警打一身之後仲要聽日報紙頭版就係衝突畫面？求下你地，大家一齊走，好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後話：<br />\n<br />\n今日總結，我認為大家要互相體諒，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制<br />\n<br />\n例如之前呢三個鐘已經去到金鐘同散咗場嘅巴打，因為擔心前線安危，加上今日目標已經達成（搶佔國際輿論），冇必要死守，所以叫走，但始終人已經唔係身處現場，冇上帝視角，望住live 仲見到咁多人，自然開始心急，語氣上亦變得唔係太好<br />\n<br />\n同時之間，前線亦想所有人平平安安走曬，自己最後一批先走，咁當然一定會有鬼從中叫人留低/ 賴死唔走，迫你留低「保護」佢哋，同樣前線亦冇上帝視角，難以判斷係手足定係鬼，加上客觀因素（現場人多電話收到嘅信號會少/ 局勢變化可能太快）散嘅速度自然亦會慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係呢一句：<br />\n永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，請大家對手足保持體諒嘅態度，兵荒馬亂之際大家嘅心情難免心急，語氣上亦會有所失儀，唯希望大家之後仍然可以再度團結，齊上齊落，打贏呢一場逆權運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d7273149f1e3d8b9cdc447eaa311022adbd4c9","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:05:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不割蓆，唯要改進</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地大家絕對唔會割蓆，但我地亦都要持續去改進，希望運動可以更上一層樓邁向成功之日，我地要一齊尊重，正如人人平等冇話邊個大啲有得話事啲，有咩提議大家投票決定，呢個亦係民主真諦，我地亦要每日一齊去檢討得失，正如人人都會有失誤嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n「是你教導我們和平示威是沒有用的」<br />\n<br />\n古今中外所有社會運動總會有失誤嘅時候，呢個係好自然亦好常見嘅事，可貴之處就係識得自省，至少我覺得今日明顯唔係end game 嘅一日，如果有朝一日真係end game 嘅係一戰竟全功嘅時候咁到時我地做乜嘢都可以，但喺呢一日來臨之前嘅過程上，我地唔可以急，仇恨係要記住因為係一股推動力，但亦要避免比仇恨支配行動，<span style=\"color: red;\">古今歷史上每一場運動係需要好長時日去完成，而且過程係一定會出現爭拗，除咗不割蓆不分化，自省改進，檢討得失，去改善下一步行動亦係成功之道。</span><br />\n<br />\n已經發生咗嘅事我地冇辦法再去改變，比人射爆隻眼真係好嬲所以我地亦冇資格去怪責甚至割蓆，但我好希望呢場運動可以成功，而呢場運動其中一樣重要嘅係自己要有一個自省精神，一旦出現失誤就要反省，反省完就要檢討，吸取教訓，下次再可以做好啲，人數亦會keep住多，人多就可以贏，如果出現失誤唔去檢討，唔尊重對方互相指罵，只會不斷重複失誤，人數會變少，最後重演2014年雨革失敗歷史。<br />\n<br />\n「後生仔應該係盡情去玩，點解佢地仲要出汗血之苦企出嚟呢？佢哋係為咗香港嘅未來呀」<br />\n<br />\n完美係一種永遠唔會達到但可以追求嘅哲學，所以我地只有不斷改善自己，互相指正，幫大家補鑊，一齊進步，一齊向成功之日進發，煲底之日我地仲要一齊慶祝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n#不割蓆<br />\n#不分化<br />\n#恆改進"},{"pid":"7349c33c725d27a8973396c73af1aa1b0f55d0a4","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"大家可以試一個聰明嘅捉鬼辦法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一發現疑似公安人員，唔洗同佢打住嘅，幫佢着件寫住「平反六四」四隻大字嘅靚衫先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （ 冇嘅可以拎支寫住「平反六四」嘅旗）然後個個人同佢笑笑口拍曬膊頭握埋手影幅大合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後任由其他記者send 上國際新聞，以及同「國內同胞」開心share <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩～原來環球時報記者係支持平反六四嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 影完相就放走佢啦，話曬佢支持平反六四喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己人嘛，客客氣氣送佢離開，佢走緊嘅時候我地仲要大聲叫「同志們辛苦了！」，受到如此高規格禮遇，對方想必喜極而泣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c2e26f9216007bc8df4fce90619b4cfd7a4a28","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:06:17.000Z","msg":"［長文但值得睇］<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">就算失望，不要絕望</span></span><br />\n<br />\n需知道自由民主思想永遠都係共產黨嘅敵人，近排香港人喺遊行、集會、街站、文宣等等工作繁多，攰就要抖下，一定要養足精神，大家唔需要自責，更加唔需要覺得無力感，甚至為此而灰心絕望<br />\n<br />\n各位要明白呢個歷史規律，喺大家都有去為民主自由而努力嘅前題之下，其實係一定會贏，只係我地唔知道幾時先會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個過程仲好可能會好漫長同有好多挫折。但最後一定會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解呢？原因好簡單，因為呢個係人類歷史發展嘅必然趨勢，舉個例，起初人類係原始部落社會，居住族群越嚟越大，慢慢出現唔同文明、秩序、分工、經濟，後來就演變成封建君主專制社會，由皇帝皇室為核心，以君主至上或者上帝嘅名義以極權去管治國家<br />\n<br />\n後來歐洲啟蒙之後神權至上嘅觀念受到挑戰，學者開始衝破傳統思維框框，思想同科技得以進步，促使民主思潮萌生，至於人類文明由君主專制時期轉變為民主自由時期，係由法國大革命開始，距離宜家已經超過200年嘅時間，我地可以睇到呢200年，有唔同民主自由制度推翻一個又一個君主專制政權，由民主制度取而代之，當然，期間都有斷斷續續出現大大小小專制嘅復辟，例如拿破崙復辟帝制，希特拉葬送魏瑪共和國，但法德兩國最終都係番返去由民主共和嘅制度下統治。<br />\n<br />\n中國亦都一樣，中華民國遷去台灣之前都叫做短暫實現過民主（1947年頒行中華民國憲法 - 1949年中華民國敗走台灣），可惜比中共打敗，自此大陸疆域嘅民主進程中斷，香港1997年之後亦直接受到中共獨裁政權嘅波及，但係，嘅然人類過去幾萬年都走唔出呢條規律，只係存在咗70年嘅中共政權又點會走得出呢條規律呢？可以預見中國最終亦會好似法德兩國咁，極權最終都會滅亡，最後都會番返去民主共和制度之下統治<br />\n<br />\n要記住，由法國大革命至今200幾年嘅時間喺成個歷史長河之中只係佔好短時間，你可以視之為過渡期，由專制到民主嘅過渡期，已經過渡咗200年，你可以睇下今日成個世界，民主政權成為咗多數，專制政權已經成為少數，而我相信，宜家嘅我地已經身處喺呢個過渡期嘅末期<br />\n<br />\n所以，全球民主化其實係歷史發展嘅必然，將來係一定會發生，前題係必須大家都要去為民主自由而努力，正如呢幾百年嘅人一樣，冇佢地嘅努力都唔會令民主得以喺世界擴散，人類歷史發展規律一直引導緊我地，我地要跟住呢個規律，各安其位，做好自己抗爭要做嘅工作，順住呢個歷史規律去走，最終我地一定會為香港帶嚟真正嘅民主自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8888d2ffc9d7c1afa4a8984788a8e5a77a4531e","tid":1485890,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:06:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44039f6c427eb93a23c9bd6ee7d624d2caf821f5","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:06:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf202fc27f9601bca9e90fcd8d02cbf90466c464","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:07:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9a8f3e849bb2e914330d7a93ae1adc242204d54","tid":1485890,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"「和」與「勇」，請對大家多點信任。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485804</a>"},{"pid":"4f98d5801a18ef643335af928eade6df0a0842c7","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"68f654ddd9eedb145f58f12cd07a4131f4802d64","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14aafb17daf91ca165249c15b8af10297420ef65","tid":1485890,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23869cea1cb75d10e4b70b3bf06a7c466f31281a","tid":1485890,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee706ab0dff80ed7669c3d9912a882892f71be43","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14aafb17daf91ca165249c15b8af10297420ef65","tid":1485890,"uid":50779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:09:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"呢個世界有77億人，減返你14億我地仲有63億人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbde7dfb676f54fd0397ddc6e28f7a3d856369a","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23869cea1cb75d10e4b70b3bf06a7c466f31281a","tid":1485890,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"我都係喺其他巴打度搵到呢條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，btw 我覺得可以用「熒幕錄影」功能先save 低條片再send上去"},{"pid":"71f90e1e1ca36ec82513654b0d5dd0e0e069a5bf","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:14:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"79a60130fb98dbe6cf7eaf7df46b5abfc50bc664","tid":1485890,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfbde7dfb676f54fd0397ddc6e28f7a3d856369a","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23869cea1cb75d10e4b70b3bf06a7c466f31281a","tid":1485890,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"我都係喺其他巴打度搵到呢條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，btw 我覺得可以用「熒幕錄影」功能先save 低條片再send上去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"ok tks"},{"pid":"bc17dcda83c01ed425b9066ed5ce4fc9de9306b5","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:16:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9d303cb1570663837f5349f565161fcdb2efd4f3","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da27775fff4f4488fed61e3fbfcfb2b030d194f","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb8578418c8e2eda8b66e1057b8fee9f0cb947f","tid":1485890,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"何韻詩post咗"},{"pid":"4328794deb1a4500847a5e73abf062f106d8ba76","tid":1485890,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:45:54.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結今晚：唔完善，可接受，但需要改善<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1485462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1485462</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3fa1389aeef7a8ab0cedcb483ad5fcc30cebc4c7","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e524f676fd85f993fa7c5f4878b8301770050d","tid":1485890,"uid":21022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eee4fc846673bbbaa7b7b8181504999db442041","tid":1485890,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:50:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"042b3c1d1ffb4cb5f9297dc3586e1d6448846e1a","tid":1485890,"uid":31710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:58:34.000Z","msg":"講得好"}]}